            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to a local report, 28-year-old Brandon Brouillard of Worcester County in Massachusetts made a plea deal on April 8 relating to his fraudulently buying a Chevy Camaro ZL1 for $83,000. The man reportedly stole the identities of two victims to pull off this stunt, instead of working hard and saving up his own money.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
